{"tid":2075211,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點可以叫朋友還錢","createTime":"2020-06-22T16:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T18:32:41.000Z","uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a21eacae00275347fe5991a629a26adadf4fb5eb","tid":2075211,"uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"話說有一日我啲朋友上咗我屋企打邊爐<br />\n佢哋話覺得好熱要開冷氣<br />\n我就話唔使啦好涼冷氣費好貴<br />\n佢哋話我哋一人比十蚊我，幫我比冷氣費<br />\n點知食完飯佢哋就拍拍囉柚走<br />\n佢哋一人爭我$10<br />\n其中一個朋友話上次車左我，要我俾返$6隧道費佢<br />\n咁即係我要問佢收返幾錢？<br />\n點先可以問佢拎返啲錢<br />\n利伸：屋企800 呎"},{"pid":"377d611107059e0219ac168c6a3b8083e5c42301","tid":2075211,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"我憑我自己能力借返黎 點解要還.jpg"},{"pid":"0f8846fcc2c7136511a8ef04884f95786989c83b","tid":2075211,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/08/24/131944_d67bb78c2296832945ab6da6fbb0edfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F08%2F24%2F131944_d67bb78c2296832945ab6da6fbb0edfc.jpg&h=c4ab9dd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a29fa2fcd04c8f63b8025cff5a8f7cc51f1991de","tid":2075211,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"偉 喺度嗎？"},{"pid":"4edd2a9240a040bb2c71ecaf8ba0a55f02a42552","tid":2075211,"uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29fa2fcd04c8f63b8025cff5a8f7cc51f1991de","tid":2075211,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"偉 喺度嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"還返$10俾我未"},{"pid":"31a0fb775484e176b99f43456ca93d5071884624","tid":2075211,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"下次去佢屋企